OL,6,FA man has been convicted of careless
OL,7,Fdriving after dashcam footage from a
OL,8,Fmember of the public caught him
OL,9,Fswerving across a road.
OL,11,FThe man was caught driving erratically
OL,12,Fand exiting his car in what appears to
OL,13,Fbe an attempt to stop and confront the
OL,14,Fdriver behind him.
OL,16,FFootage from Avon and Somerset Police
OL,17,Fthen shows the driver's vehicle
OL,18,Fhalting abruptly.
