OL,6,FIt was submitted to the force as part
OL,7,Fof Operation Snap, a nationwide
OL,8,Fcampaign launched to make it easier
OL,9,Ffor drivers to submit evidence of poor
OL,10,Fdriving to the police.
OL,12,FThe driver appeared at Bath
OL,13,FMagistrates Court in the first week of
OL,14,FApril where he received a fine and
OL,15,Fnine points on his licence.
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Roads Policing Unit
OL,18,Fsaid: "Last week, a man was convicted
OL,19,Fof careless driving at Bath
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court.
